" disable arrows keys because I want to force myself to get used to hjkl
" navigation
" Disable Arrow keys in Escape mode
map <up> <nop>
map <down> <nop>
map <left> <nop>
map <right> <nop>

" Disable Arrow keys in Insert mode
imap <up> <nop>
imap <down> <nop>
imap <left> <nop>
imap <right> <nop>

" get rid of shift ; to get to : commands
nnoremap ; :

